description: Las Vegas hot dog fans have found their haven, and that’s GALS Hot Dogs. With an offering of gourmet hot dogs and a diverse selection of tasty toppings, it’s no wonder this cart is a local favorite. Travel the nation with one delicious creation at a time like the Cali Dog, The Chicago Dog, and The Big Texan with tangy BBQ sauce. And don’t forget to cool off from that Nevada sunshine with a delightfully sweet and refreshing sno cone. GALS is generally located in the lot of Count’s Kustoms, but if you’ve got a big party or event coming up, you’ve gotta have this cool cart come cater.
name: GALS Hot Dogs
